  objectiveLabels:
  - Shanti ki emergency condition samjhein
  - Emergency transport aur receipt confirm karein
  - Triage desk par Shanti ki medical history dein
  - Emergency consent ko padhkar signed copy lein
  - Helpers Hand verified donor network activate karein
  - Pharmacy stock register aur issue time verify karein
  - Medicine batch label aur invoice mismatch preserve karein
  - Duty doctor se private medical update lein
  - Verified case file ya instant public post chunein
